  "detailed_description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>A bicycle road trip</strong>: Explore a new world and wind your way through stunning landscapes on your bicycle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695330/extras/9de9f7dc19d07e1d57270dd94cbd0281.poster.avif?t=1767129392\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695330/extras/9de9f7dc19d07e1d57270dd94cbd0281.webm?t=1767129392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695330/extras/9de9f7dc19d07e1d57270dd94cbd0281.mp4?t=1767129392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Document, photograph, and record</strong>: Collect memories, make recordings and capture the most important moments from the current season to preserve them for future generations.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695330/extras/207a85996742b086c1432b6a1bf1cc54.poster.avif?t=1767129392\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695330/extras/207a85996742b086c1432b6a1bf1cc54.webm?t=1767129392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695330/extras/207a85996742b086c1432b6a1bf1cc54.mp4?t=1767129392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>A highly customizable journal</strong>: Piece together the secrets of the world of SEASON before a cataclysm washes everything away.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695330/extras/5a93e1dd5bf84acb2ffc8400dd500337.poster.avif?t=1767129392\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695330/extras/5a93e1dd5bf84acb2ffc8400dd500337.webm?t=1767129392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695330/extras/5a93e1dd5bf84acb2ffc8400dd500337.mp4?t=1767129392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Emotionally complex characters</strong>: Meet a diverse cast of characters, each of whom has two precious things to share with you: the stories of their lives and a moment together at the end of the season.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695330/extras/06aff83e13d0213d2496f9db6843891f.poster.avif?t=1767129392\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695330/extras/06aff83e13d0213d2496f9db6843891f.webm?t=1767129392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695330/extras/06aff83e13d0213d2496f9db6843891f.mp4?t=1767129392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>A compelling narrative</strong>: This quest leads you to the big questions: what is this season? Why is it ending? And what will the next season bring?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695330/extras/0c8958016822e8f95f4e980e48d9e215.poster.avif?t=1767129392\" width=598 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695330/extras/0c8958016822e8f95f4e980e48d9e215.webm?t=1767129392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695330/extras/0c8958016822e8f95f4e980e48d9e215.mp4?t=1767129392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
